                    <lb n="5" break="no"/>-k koṭumoṉmaiyil U
                    <lb n="6" break="no"/>ṭaiyār tiruvarattuṟai y-u⌈
                    <lb n="7" break="no"/><unclear>ṭaiya</unclear> nāyaṉār kōy<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>lukku nā
