                    <lb n="9" break="no"/>kaḷil Uṭaiya-nāyakaṉ-āṉa tē
                    <lb n="10" break="no"/>vāram-aḻakiyāṉ vāṇa-rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ṉ
                    <lb n="11"/>Āṭkoṇṭa-nāyakarum nācci<unclear>ya</unclear>
                    <lb n="12" break="no"/>rum <hi rend="grantha">prabhai</hi>yum tiruvātavūr-pe
                    <lb n="13" break="no"/><supplied reason="lost">ru</supplied>māḷaiyum Eḻunt-a<unclear>ru</unclear>ḷivittar
